@startuml DFD_Level0_Context_Diagram
!define RECTANGLE class

skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

' External Entities
actor "Pet Owner" as Owner <<External Entity>>
actor "Veterinarian" as Vet <<External Entity>>
actor "Caregiver/Seller" as Caregiver <<External Entity>>
database "OpenStreetMap API" as OSM <<External System>>
database "Groq LLM API" as Groq <<External System>>
database "Firebase Cloud Messaging" as FCM <<External System>>

' Main System
rectangle "PawPal\nPet Care Management System" as PawPal <<Process 0>>

' Data Flows
Owner --> PawPal : User Credentials\nPet Information\nHealth Queries\nAppointment Requests\nPet Photos
PawPal --> Owner : Authentication Token\nBreed Predictions\nHealth Guidance\nAppointment Confirmations\nNotifications

Vet --> PawPal : Clinic Information\nAvailability Slots\nAppointment Status
PawPal --> Vet : Appointment Requests\nPet Medical History\nNotifications

Caregiver --> PawPal : Service Listings\nProduct Catalog
PawPal --> Caregiver : Order Details\nService Requests

PawPal --> OSM : GPS Coordinates\nClinic Search Query
OSM --> PawPal : Nearby Clinics Data

PawPal --> Groq : Contextualized Query\nPet Profile
Groq --> PawPal : AI-Generated Response

PawPal --> FCM : Notification Payload\nUser Tokens
FCM --> PawPal : Delivery Status

note right of PawPal
  Context Level (Level 0)
  Shows the entire PawPal system
  as a single process with all
  external entities and data flows
end note

@enduml
